How to install docekr-container in Linux Machines:

OS : RHEL
Download the docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io
Create local repo and install packages:
       yum install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io
Start and enable the service
      systemctl enable docker.service
      systemctl start docker.service
      systemctl status docker.service
      docker version / docekr --version
      docker info
      
OS: Ubuntu:
      apt-get update
      apt-get install docker-ce docker-ce-cli containerd.io  / apt-get install docker.io
      docker version
      systemctl enable docker.service
      systemctl start docker.service
      systemctl status docker.service
      docker info
      
 OS: SUSE
       zyppper install apt-transport-https curl -y
       zypper install -y docker
       systemctl enable docker.service
       systemctl start docker.service
       systemctl status docker.service
       docker version / docker --version
